Heather Tom https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heather_Tom 0 Heather Marie Tom (born November 4, 1975) is an American actress best known for her work on various soap operas, with her best known roles being Victoria Newman on The Young and the Restless, Kelly Cramer on One Life to Live and, since 2007, Katie Logan on The Bold and the Beautiful.
